\rcrd MRK 0
\id MRK Sena of Mozambique
\h Marku
\mt Mphangwa zadidi ninga mudazilembera Marku
\rcrd MRK 1
\c 1
\s Kumwabza kwa mphangwa na Djuwau Batixta
\p
\vref MRK.1:1
\v 1
\vt Kutoma kwa mphangwa zadidi za yezu kirixtu,mwana wa Mulungu.
\vref MRK.1:2
\v 2
\vt Atoma ninga mudazilembera mporofeta wa Mulungu Izaya kuti: Ndinatuma mwanankati wanga pasogolo pako toera kukusasanyira njira.
\vref MRK.1:3
\v 3
\vt Iyi ndi fala ya ule anakhuwa n'thando mbalonga:Sasanyirani njira ya mbuya na kundendemeza miseu yace.
\vref MRK.1:4
\v 4
\vt Ndi tenepa kubulukira kudacita Djuwau Batixta n'thando, mbakhapasa anthu batixmu na kuapanga tenepa:Chunyukani mbamusanduza mitima yanu toera Mulungu a kulekelereni kudawa kwanu.'
\vref MRK.1:5
\v 5
\vt Anthu onsene a ku Djudeya na a ku Djerusalema akhaenda kuna Djuwau Batixta,kabweka kudawa kwawo penepo Djuwau Batixta akhaapasa batixmo n'nyanza ya Djordani.
\vref MRK.1:6
\v 6
\vt Djuwau akhabvala nguwo za nthembe za cinyama cinacemerwa kamero mbakhamanga bhande ya nthembe n'cuno mwace mbakhandya nthete na uci wa n'tsanga.
\vref MRK.1:7
\v 7
\vt Mbakhalonga tenepa kuna mbumba kuti:'Nduli mwanga anabwera ana mphambvu zakupiringana ine pontho ine sine munthu wakukwanisa kunkotamira toera kunsudzula mithambo ya nsapato zace.
\vref MRK.1:8
\v 8
\vt Ine ndakupasani batixmu na madzi.Mbwenye Iye anakupasani batixmu na nzimu wa mulungu.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:9
\v 9
\vt Pa ntsiku zenizo yezu akhabuluka kucisa ca Nazareti ku dziku ya Galileya mbaenda kukapasiwa batixmu na Djuwau Batixta mu nyanza ya Djordani.
\vref MRK.1:1
\v 1a
\vt Pa ndzidzi udapandira yezu m'madzi iye aona thambo yafunguka na tenepa ndzimu wa Mulungu,ninga nkhangaiwa, mbukhachita mbumphamira.
\rem <error ref="41001001" text="1a" />Verse number (or previous one) is out of order
\vref MRK.1:11
\v 11
\vt Penepo, kudzulu kwabveka fala mbilonga kuti:Iwe ndiwe mwananga wakufunika.Muna iwe ndisabva kusanzaya.
\vref MRK.1:12
\v 12
\vt Pakumala penepyo Yezu akumbizwa na ndzimu wa Mulungu kuenda n'thando.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:13
\v 13
\vt Na tenepa Yezu akhala n'thando ntsiku makumanai mbakhaleserwa na Sathani. Yezu akhakhala pakati pa pinyama pya nsanga. mbwenye atumwi ace abwera kam'phatira.
\vref MRK.1:14
\v 14
\vt Pidamala Djuwau Batixta kupita n'kaidi,Yezu abwerera ku Galileya kalonga mphangwa zadidi za Mulungu,mbakhalonga tenepa:
\vref MRK.1:15
\v 15
\vt Ndzidzi wakwana. Umambo wa Mulungu uli dhuzi chunyukani kudawa kwanu,mutawire mphangwa zadidi.
\vref MRK.1:16
\v 16
\vt Yezu mukhapita iye na mumbale mwa Bara ya Galileya aona anyakokota awiri mu ubale mwawo mbakhagwisira kokota yawo. M'bara madzina awo anacemerwa Simao na Andereya.
\vref MRK.1:17
\v 17
\vt Yezu a apanga tenepa: Nditowereni ndinakucitani anyakokota a anthu.
\vref MRK.1:18
\v 18
\vt Iwo padzidzi ubozdi ene asiya makokota awo mbatowera Yezu.
\vref MRK.1:19
\v 19
\vt Pakufamba pang'ono pasogolo Yezu aona Tiago Djakobo na Djuwau, ana a zebedeu; mbakhathunka makoota awo m'mwadiya.
\vref MRK.1:20
\v 20
\vt Yezu aacemera. Penepo pene iwo ansiya babawawo na anyabasa ace m'mwadia, iwo mbaenda mbatowera Yezu.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:21
\v 21
\vt Pakumala Yezu na anyakupfunza ace aenda ku ndzinda wa kafaranaumi. Nsabudu mwace ya kuphembera, mbatoma kupfunzisa.
\vref MRK.1:22
\v 22
\vt Anthu akhamubva mapfunzisiro ace akhadzumatirwa napyo, thangwi iye akhalonga tayu ninga anyakuziwisa a mwambo, mbwenye ninga n'tongi.
\vref MRK.1:23
\v 23
\vt Pa ndzidzi unowu abulukira pa nyumba ya kuphembera mamuna m'bodzi akhali na uzimu wa kuipa. iye akhakhuwa kmbakhalonga kuna Yezu kuti:
\vref MRK.1:24
\v 24
\vt Iwe Yezu wa ku kunazareti usafunanji kuna ife? Wabwera kudza katifudza kidi? Ine ndisadziwa kuti Iwe ndiwe wakulungama adatumiwa na Mulungu!
\vref MRK.1:25
\v 25
\vt Yezu am'pwekera nzimu wakuipa mbam'panga:matama! buluka muna munthu uyu!
\vref MRK.1:26
\v 26
\vt Nzimu uyu wakuipa am'bhoma mamuna na mphambvu zonsene, mbakhuwa mbabuluka muna iye mamuna.
\vref MRK.1:27
\v 27
\vt Anthu onsene adzumtirwa napyo, mbabvuuna okha-okha: Ninji penepi?Cipfunzo ici n'chipsa.Mbwenye cirikupfunziswa na mphambvu za munthu wakutonga. Thangwi asaikha mwambo ace kuna mizimu ya kuipa, iyo mbimbvera.
\vref MRK.1:28
\v 28
\vt Na tenepa mbiri yace Yezu yabalalika na mwansanga mu dziko yonsene Galileya.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:29
\v 29
\vt Kubuluka penepo Yezu abuluka mu nyumba ya kuphembera mbaenda pabodzi na Tiyago na Djuwau, kunyumba kwa Simau Pedhuru na Andereya.
\vref MRK.1:30
\v 30
\vt Penepo anthu ampanga Yezu kuti mebzalace wace Simau asagona na kudwala.
\vref MRK.1:31
\v 31
\vt Yezu aenda pakhakhala iye mbam'phata manja ace mbam'pheza kumulamusa. Na tenepa nthenda yamulekeratu yawangiratu. Iye mbatoma kuaphatira basa.
\vref MRK.1:33
\v 33
\vt Anthu onsene a mundzinda akhadagumanyana pa nsuo wa nyumba ikhadafikira Yezu /ikhakhala Yezu.
\vref MRK.1:34
\v 34
\vt Yezu akonza/ awangisa nthenda zakusiyana-siyana za anthu azinji na kuthamangisambo mizimu yakuipa mizinji.Iyo ikhanziwa mbani Yezu. ndi thangwi eneyo Yezu aakhondesa kulonga / kuti alonge.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:35
\v 35
\vt Na macibese mukhacita manga nkhaa, Yezu alamuka mbaenda n'thando kaphembera.
\vref MRK.1:36
\v 36
\vt Simau Pehuru aenda na anzace kasaka Yezu.
\vref MRK.1:37
\v 37
\vt Na tenepa iwo pidan'gumanawo alonga tenepa: Anthu asakusaka/Anthu azinji...
\vref MRK.1:38
\v 38
\vt Yezu aapanga tenepa:Tendeni m'pisa pinangopya dhuzi-dhuzi, toera ndaafokotozerembo mphangwa zadidi.Thangwi ndazera/ndabwerera penepyo.
\vref MRK.1:39
\v 39
\vt Yezu akhaenda mbuto zonsene za Galileya, mbakhalonga mphangwa zadidi m'manyumba a kuphembera,na kubulusa mizimu yakuipa.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.1:40
\v 40
\vt Penepo abwera mamuna m'bodzi wamatanya kuna Yezu mbam'godamira mba'phemba tenepa:Mungafuna,ndikhafuna mundiwangise''
\vref MRK.1:41
\v 41
\vt Yezu am'bvera nsisi zikulu mbafutula manja ace mbam'gwesa mbampanga: Ndisafuna, nthenda yako mbiwange/wawanga.
\vref MRK.1:42
\v 42
\vt Pa ndzidzi ubodzi ene mamuna awanga.
\vref MRK.1:43
\v 43
\vt Na tenepo ampwekera mbamuendesa.
\vref MRK.1:44
\v 44
\vt Mbampanga kuti:Leka kupanga munthu penepyo.pakotoma ndoko ukadingwe kuna nyantsembe/kuna nyantsembe toera akundinge. Ungamala uperekentsembe idalinga Mozesi,toera anthu aziwe kuti iwe wawangadi.
\vref MRK.1:45
\v 45
\vt Mbwenye mamuna uyu pidabuluka iye penepo atoma kulonga pakweca pyonsene pidacitika. Natenepa mphangwa zamwadzika monsene, na tenepa Yezu akhacimwana kupita m'pisa na kusanzaya. Akhakhala kunja m'mbuto za kubisala.Mbwenye anthu akhabuluka m'mbuto zinsene kwenda kansaka.
\rcrd MRK 2
\c 2
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.2:1
\v 1
\vt Pakupita ntsiku pan'gono,Yezu abwerera pontho kukafarnau. Pidabva iwo kuti Yezu aly panyumba,
\vref MRK.2:2
\v 2
\vt Agumanykana mwinji wa anthu mbakafinyana pansuo na thangwi yakusoeka kwa mbuto. Yezu pikafunzisa iye phangwa zadidi.
\vref MRK.2:3
\v 3
\vt Amuna anai am'bwerera nyanfutete m'bodzi.
\vref MRK.2:4
\v 4
\vt Mbwenye iwo akhacimwana pita na mpaka fika kna Yezu, na thangwi ya mwinji wa anthu.Akwira pa tsoi, ku kundu ikhakhala Yezu, mbatchitisa na penepo akhaluneresa iwo pa khangala.
\vref MRK.2:5
\v 5
\vt Yezu pidaona iye cikhulupiriro cikhali na anthu awa, alonga tenepa:kuti ntenda mwananga, kudawa kako kwalekererwa.
\vref MRK.2:6
\v 6
\vt Mbwenyeanyakudziwisa a mwambo akhakhala penepo,pidabva iwo penepyo akhalonga okhene tenepa:
\vref MRK.2:7
\v 7
\vt Thangwi yanji mamuna uyu asakwanisa longa tenepa? Iye asxola Mulungu!
\vref MRK.2:8
\v 8
\vt Mbwenye Yezu nakudziwa manyerezero awo,aabvunza:thangwi yanji musanyerezera tenepa nkati mwanu?
\vref MRK.2:9
\v 9
\vt Phyanji pinakhonda nensa kulonga kuna nyanfutete:'Kudawa kwako kwalekererwa'peno ndipange:Lamuka, kwata khangala yako uende ku nyumbakwako?
\vref MRK.2:10
\v 10
\vt Dziwani mphapo kuti mwana munthu anmphabvu zakulekerera kudawa pantsi pano.
\vref MRK.2:11
\v 11
\vt Azun 'gunuka kuna nyanfutete mbampanga:lamuka, kwata khangala yako, uende ku nyumba kwako.
\vref MRK.2:12
\v 12
\vt Mamuna alamuka na mwasanga, akwata khangala yace mbaenda pyace, anthu ansenembamuona. Onsene adzumatirwa napyo /na ipyo na pidaona iyo,mbapasa mbiri Mulungu mbalonga:'Cipo tasati kupiona pinthu ninga ipi!
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.2:13
\v 13
\vt Yezu abwera pontho mbaenda ku gombe ya Bara Galileya. Anthu aenda mbasaka mpaka kweneko ,iye mbakhaafunzisa.
\vref MRK.2:14
\v 14
\vt Pikhabwerera iye aona Levi ,mwana wa Alifeu, akhali nawa pa nyumba ikhakumbuswa misoklho,mbampanga:'Nditowere!'Levi alamuka mbatowera.
\vref MRK.2:15
\v 15
\vt Ntsiku inango Yezu akhadya pabodzina anyakufunza ace kunyumba kwa Levi;akhalipombo pabodzi na anyakukumbusa misokho na anthu azinji anyakudawa akhantoera.
\vref MRK.2:16
\v 16
\vt Anyakudzwisa a mwambo,na afarisi,pikhaona iwo kuti Yezu ali kudya pabodzi na anthu anewa,abvunzisa kuna anyafunza ace:'Thangwi yanji iye asadya pabodzi na anyamisokho na anthu anyakudawa?
\vref MRK.2:17
\v 17
\vt Yezu mudabva iyepenepyo aatawira:'Angumi andasoa nthenda/anyakuwanga nkhabe saka nyakukodza. Mbwenye anbva kuplh/ntenda ndiye anasaka nyakukonza. Ine sidabwera kudza kacemara adidi tay, mbwenye ale anyakudawa.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.2:18
\v 18
\vt Ntsiinango anyakufunza a Djuwau Batixta na afarisi akhamphembera/mbakhamana cakudya/na njala mbakhonda cakudya, aoneka mbozdi mbaenda kabvunza Yezu: Ndi thangwi yanji anyakufunza a Djuwau na afarisi asamphembera na njala mbakhonda cakudya, ako mbakhonda citambo tenepo?
\vref MRK.2:19
\v 19
\vt Yezu aatawira tenepa:Pisacitika kuti adacemerwa kuphwandu ya macunguzo akhale potho mbadasukwala mphale wace anafuna kucunguzwa mbali na awene? Nkhabe citika.
\vref MRK.2:2
\v 2
\vt O Mbwenye zinafunika ntsiku zinzfuna iwo kukwatirwa mpale pakati pawo. tsiku zenezi iwo anati apinanse kusiya pyakudya.
\rem <error ref="41002002" text="2" />Verse number (or previous one) is out of order
\vref MRK.2:21
\v 21
\vt Nkhabe munthu anaikha cigamba ca nguwo ipsa pa nguwo yakusala. Thangwi cigamba cipsa cinathimiza pandula nguwo yakusakala piringana kalene.
\vref MRK.2:22
\v 22
\vt Pontho nkhabe citika kukwata vinyu ipsa mbuikha nkhali zakuizira kale/zakuwirisila kale,gopera vinhu ipsa ingawira inadza kakuka mbiswa nkhali, mbauluza nkhali na vinhu ene. Mbwenye vinhu ipsa isafunika inkhiwembo pipsa.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.2:23
\v 23
\vt Ntsiku inango ya Sabudu,Yezu na anyakufunza ace akhapita na pakati pa munda.Pikhaenda iwo anyakufunza ace atoma kusaka pyakudya adye.
\vref MRK.2:24
\v 24
\vt Mbwenye afarisi abvunzisa Yezu kuti:'Kodi ndithangwi yanji anyakufunza ako asacita pire pinakhondesa mwambo'sikupicita ntsiku ya Sabudu?
\vref MRK.2:25
\v 25
\vt Mbwenye uye aatawira tenepa: Kodi imwe mudaoona pidalembiwa na thangwi ya pidacita mambo Dhavidi na amuna ace ntsiku inango pikhakhala iwo na njala mbasoa cakudya?
\vref MRK.2:26
\v 26
\vt Apita n'ýumba ya Mulungu, pa dzidzi ukhakhala Abiatari ninga nkhulu wa nyentsembe, mbadya iye na anzace mikate ikadaikhirwa ntsembe Mulungu.Mbwenye mwambo usalonga kuti mikate eneyo isadywa na anyantsembe basi.
\vref MRK.2:27
\v 27
\vt Iye athimiza na kuapanga tenepa:'Sabudo ninga ntsiku yakupuma, yacitirwa anthu, mbwenye anthu hadacitirwa Sabudu tayu.
\vref MRK.2:28
\v 28
\vt Na thangwi eneyo, mwana munthu asantoga nantsiku ya sabudu ene.
\rcrd MRK 3
\c 3
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.3:1
\v 1
\vt Sabudu yace inango Yezu apita mu nyumba ya kuphembera. Mwenemo agumana mamuna m'bodzi na manja a nfutete.
\vref MRK.3:2
\v 2
\vt Mbwenye akhagumanika / akhalipo mwenemu anango akhafuna kusumira Yezu kuti asanumpha /asapwadza mwambo wa mozesi na thangwi eneyo iwo akhamulanganisa ngakhala anamuwangisa ntsiku ya sabudu.
\vref MRK.3:3
\v 3
\vt Penepo Yezu apanga mamuna wakulamala djnja/manja kuti: Lamuka, bwera pano pakati.
\vref MRK.3:4
\v 4
\vt Pakumala Yezu abvunza akhamulang'anisa kuti: Ndi ninji cinatawirira mwambo wathu ntsiku za sabudu:Kucita udidi peno uipi?kupulumusa munthu peno kumumpha?Mbenye nkhabe munthu adantawira.
\vref MRK.3:5
\v 5
\vt Na tenepo Yezu aalang'ana na kusiribza pontho na kutsukwala, thangwi akhali anthu akuumamitima. Pakumalapenepo ampangan'tenda:Futhula manja ako.Iye afuthula pandzidzi ubidzi ene munthu /n'tenda awanga.
\vref MRK.3:6
\v 6
\vt Penepo afarisi abuluka pa nyumba ya kuphembera mbaenda mwansanga kagumana na nkumbi wa Herodi toera kusaka njira yakapha mayo Yezu.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.3:7
\v 7
\vt Na tenepo Yezu abuluka mbaenda nkundu mwa bara ya Galileya na anyakupfunza ace. Anthu azinji a ku Galileya akhantoera.
\vref MRK.3:8
\v 8
\vt Akhantoerambo anthu anango azinji a ku Djudeya,a ku Djerusalema, a ku Idumeya, a n'tunda unango wa nyanza Djordani, a ku dziko ya tiro na ya Sidoni Anthu onsene.fs
\vref MRK.3:9
\v 9
\vt Yezu aphemba anyafhunza ace kuti ansakiremwadiya,toera akhonde kufhinyiwa na mbumba.
\vref MRK.3:10
\v 10
\vt Ndimo mwene, Yezu akhonda wangisa anthu onsene akhakhala na nthenda zawo za kusiyana-siyana, akhaenda kuna Iye toera kun'gwesa/ iwo an'gweze.
\vref MRK.3:11
\v 11
\vt Na tenepa ale akhali na mizimu ya kuipa, na kuona Yezu akhan'gwera pa myendo pace na kukhuwa tenepa:"Iwe ndiwe mwana wa mulungu."
\vref MRK.3:12
\v 12
\vt Mbwenye Yezu aakhondesa na mphambvu zonsene kuti akhonde kumulonga.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.3:13
\v 13
\vt Kubuluka penepo Yezu akwira pa phiri mbacemera ale akhafuna iye kusakhula abwere dhudzi na Iye. Na tenepo iwo abwera/an'fendezera.
\vref MRK.3:14
\v 14
\vt Na tenepo Yezu asnkhula n'tsoka/ ntsoka wa khumi na awiri toera afambe na iye na kuwatuma kwenda mbamwaza mphangwa zadidi.
\vref MRK.3:15
\v 15
\vt Pontho na kuwapasa mpambvu za kuthamangisa mizimu yakuipa.Anawa aziwika na dzina ya anyakufhunza.
\vref MRK.3:16
\v 16
\vt Madzina awo mbawa: Simau, anacemerwa na Pedhuru,
\vref MRK.3:17
\v 17
\vt Tiyago/Djakobi,ana a Zebedeu, iwo asaziwika na dzina ya Boanerijes. Kweneko nkhubveka mwanawa ndjazi.
\vref MRK.3:18
\v 18
\vt Andereya, Filipi, Bartulomeu,Mateu, Tomee, Tiyago,-mwana wa Alufeu, Tadeu, Simau, wa nsoka wa kananea,
\vref MRK.3:19
\v 19
\vt Pintho na Djuda kariote, ule adasandukira Yezu /adadza kasandukira Yezu adamalisira kusandukura Yezu.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.3:20
\v 20
\vt Padzidzi unango Yezu apita mu nyumba ibodzi:Mwenemu agumanyikana pontho mwinji wa anthu. Na tenepa Yezu na anyakufhunza ace aacimwana kudya.
\vref MRK.3:21
\v 21
\vt Abale ace Yezu pidabva iwo penepyo aenda kankwata,thangwi pakati pawo akhalipo akhalonga kuti Yezu ali kudwala ntenda wa n'sala.
\vref MRK.3:22
\v 22
\vt Anyakuziwisa anango a mwambo akhadabuluka ku Djerusalema akhalonga kuti:Yezu ana belizebu/sathani. Anango ndiwo akhalonga kuti:Ndi nkulu wa madimonyo ndiye anampasa mphambvu zakuthamangisa madimonyo anango.
\vref MRK.3:23
\v 23
\vt Na tenepa Yezu acemera anthu onsene mbabwera kuna iye, mbaapanga na mitsanjikuti:Sathani anabulusika ekha ene.
\vref MRK.3:24
\v 24
\vt Umambo ungagawika, mbumenyana okha-okha unamalisira kufudzika.
\vref MRK.3:25
\v 25
\vt N'kati mwa abale mungaoneka kugawana, ubale unowu unamalisira kufudzika.
\vref MRK.3:26
\v 26
\vt Na tenepa sathani angamenyeka/angapimenyeka ekha, umambo wace mbugawika iye nkhabe kukhala m'aso. Pontho umambo wace unafudzika.
\vref MRK.3:27
\v 27
\vt Nkhabe munthu anakwanisa kupita n'nyumba yamamunawa mpambvu toera kum'bera pinthu piyace. Angafuna mbatome kum'manga. Angamala penepo anakodza kum'bera pinthu pyace.
\vref MRK.3:28
\v 28
\vt Ndimo mwene ndinakupangani kuti: Kuti asalekerera pyonsene pinacitira Munthu. kudawa/madawipeno kuxola.
\vref MRK.3:29
\v 29
\vt Mbwenye ule anxola nzimu wa mulungu nkhabe kulekererwa. Thangwi manthangwi ace nkhabe kumala/mbakukhale kwenda na kwenda.
\vref MRK.3:30
\v 30
\vt Yezu alonga ipi thangwi anango akhalonga kuti Iye ana mizimu yakuipa.
\s Subtítulo
\p
\vref MRK.3:31
\v 31
\vt Penepo mai na abale ace yezu afika mbacemeresa Yezu/mban'cemeresa kunja.
\vref MRK.3:32
\v 32
\vt Akhalipo anthu azinji n'khundu mwa Yezu. Penepo anango ampanga kuti: "Mai wako naabale ako ali kunja uku, asafuna kulonga na imwe/asasaka imwe /asakusakani"
\vref MRK.3:33
\v 33
\vt Na tenepa Yezu aatawira kuti: Mbani mai wanga, mbani abale anga?/Mbani mai wanga na abale anga?
\vref MRK.3:34
\v 34
\vt Penepo Yezu alang'ana anthu akhali na iye n'khundu mwace mbalonga tenepa:Awa ndiwo mai" wanga" na abale anga/ mai wanga na abale anga mbawa.
\vref MRK.3:35
\v 35
\vt Thangwi munthu onsene ancita kufuna kwa Mulungu, unowu ndiye mwana mamuna nzanga, mwana nkadzi wanga na mai mai wanga /m'bale wanga wa mamuna, mbale wanga wanga nkadzi na mai wanga / mbale wanga,mwana ukadzi wanga na mai wanga./... abale anga amuna na akadzi na mai wanga.
\rcrd MRK 4
\c 4
\s
\p
\vref MRK.4:1
\v 1
\vt Yezu atoma pontho kufunzisa n'gombe mwa bara ya Galileya . Mbwenye mwinji wa anthu ukhanzungulira na thangwi eneyo Yezu apakira m; mwadia mbakhala pansi, mbasia mwinji wa anthu n'gombe .
\vref MRK.4:2
\v 2
\vt Yezu atoma kuafunzisa na misanje, pinthu pizinji . Iye akhalonga tenepa:
\vref MRK.4:3
\v 3
\vt Bveserani! Ntsiku inango mamuna m; bodzi aenda kabzwala kumunda kwace.
\vref MRK.4:4
\v 4
\vt Mukhabwala iye, mbeu inango yagwa nkhundu mwa njira, mbalame mbaidzokhona.
\vref MRK.4:5
\v 5
\vt Inango yagwa pamataka anamiala. Mbeu eneyo yamera na muansanga thangwe mataka akhadacepa.
\vref MRK.4:6
\v 6
\vt Mbwenye pidagaka dzwa, yamala kupya thangwi mitchichi ikhadacepa
\vref MRK.4:7
\v 7
\vt Mbeu inango yagwa pakati paminga, minga yakula mbaibvula mbeu. Na nthangwi eneyo yacimwana kubala misapo.
\vref MRK.4:8
\v 8
\vt Mbwnye mbeu inango yagwa pa mataka adidieneyo yamera mbaikula, mbaibala misapo makumatatu, makumatanthatu mpaka kufika dzana pa mbeu ibodzi.
\vref MRK.4:9
\v 9
\vt Pakumalisa Yezu alonga tenepa: «Ana makutu akubva, mbabvesese!»
\vref MRK.4:10
\v 10
\vt Pidamala mwazika anthu, anango akhadasala abvungazikana na anyakufunza ace,mbaphembakuna Yezu kuti aapange usalanganji nsanji uyu.
\vref MRK.4:11
\v 11
\vt Yezu aapanga tenepa:« Kuli imwe Mulungu afuna kukudziwisani pyakubisala pya ufumu wace,mbwnye kuli anthu a kunja pyonsene anapifunziswa na misanje.
\vref MRK.4:12
\v 12
\vt Toera kuti alan'gane mbakhonda kwona,abve mbakhonda kupibvesesa. Thangwi angapicita penepyo azungunuka kuna Mulungu iye mbaalekererakundawa kwawo.
\vref MRK.4:13
\v 13
\vt Yezu aatawiza tenepa:«Ngakhala imwe nkhabe kubvesesa nsanje uyu anthu anango ananbvesatany?
\vref MRK.4:14
\v 14
\vt Nyakubzwala, asabwala fala ya mulungu.
\vref MRK.4:15
\v 15
\vt Mbeu zidagwa mbale mwa njira ndi ale adabva fala, mbwenye asabwera Sathani mbabulusa fala ikhadabzwala nkati mwa iyo.
\vref MRK.4:16
\v 16
\vt Anthu anango alandana na mbeu idagwa pamataka anamiala,asitambira fala wakukomerwa.
\vref MRK.4:17
\v 17
\vt Mbwenye nkhabe mitchichi mizinji.nyatwa zingagwera, peno angatchingwa na thangwi ya fala ya Mulungu, asasia pyawo.
\vref MRK.4:18
\v 18
\vt Anango alandana na mbeu idagwa pakati paminga. Anthu awa asabva mphangwa zadidi za Mulungu.
\vref MRK.4:19
\v 19
\vt Mbwenye na thangwi ya kusaka udidi wa padziko, ponto na kufuna kufhuma, na pizinji pinango pyakusirira, pisalasa fala mbaicimwana kubala misapo
\vref MRK.4:20
\v 20
\vt Mbwenye anthu anango alandana na mbeu idagwa pamataka adidi: Asabva mphangwa zadidi za Mulungu, mbazibala misapo inango makumatatu,inango makumatanthatu inango dzana pa mbeu ibadzi.
\vref MRK.4:21
\v 21
\vt Yezu athimiza nakuafunzisa pontho tenepa:«Alipo munthu agasa nyale mbaigudumira na n'goro peno mbaikha pantsi pa talimba?Nkhabe asayikha pakweca toera imwynike pyadidi.
\vref MRK.4:22
\v 22
\vt Na tenepa pyonsene pidabiswa pinati pioneke na pire pyonsene pinacitwa n'chibisobiso pinati.
\vref MRK.4:23
\v 23
\vt Ana makutu mbabve.
\vref MRK.4:24
\v 24
\vt Yezu alonga pontho tenepa:«Bvesesane pyadidi pinakupangani ine! Na combo cinapima na imwe anzanu cibadzi-bodzi Mulungu anakupimanimbo naco, panango piringana penepi:
\vref MRK.4:25
\v 25
\vt Thangwi ule anapyo pizinji, anatambira pinango, mbenye ule anapyo pan'gono, anapokoswa na pire pinango pyene pina iye!
\vref MRK.4:26
\v 26
\vt Yezu athimiza pontho kulonga tenepa:m'bodzi adabzwala mbeu m'munda mwace.
\vref MRK.4:27
\v 27
\vt Iye asagona mbalamuka ntsiku zonsene masikuna masikati, mbeu isamera mbaikula, mbwenye iye nkhabe kupidziwa kuti pisacitika tani penepi.
\vref MRK.4:28
\v 28
\vt Thangwi mataka asamera okha ene mbeu pakutoma asabulukira masamba, thimize asanthumburuka, pakumaliza asabala mbeu.
\vref MRK.4:29
\v 29
\vt Mbeu zingatokota anthu asazibvuna thangwi wafika ndzidzi wa kubvuna.
\vref MRK.4:30
\v 30
\vt Yezu akhathimiza basi na kulonga tenepa:«Tinaulandanisa nanji umambo wa Mulungu? tinausangiza na wsanje wanji?
\vref MRK.4:31
\v 31
\vt Walandana na mbeu ya mustarda, iyo ndi in'gono piringana mbeu zonsene za pantsi pano.
\vref MRK.4:32
\v 32
\vt Mbenye ingabzwalwa mbaimera isakula piringana miti inango; isakhala na thawi zikulu, mbalame za kudzulu mbazikwanisa manga ntsanza mwenemu.
\vref MRK.4:33
\v 33
\vt Yezu akafunzisa mbumba na misanje ninga iyi toera kuti apibvesese mwadidi .
\vref MRK.4:34
\v 34
\vt Kazinji kene akhaapanga na misanje, mbwenye angakhala ekha na anyakufunza ace basi, akaatchululira pyonsenene.
\vref MRK.4:35
\v 35
\vt Ntsiku eneyo, na masikati, Yezu apanga anyakufunza ace:«Tiwambukeni tiende ntunda ule wa bara.»
\vref MRK.4:36
\v 36
\vt Iwo aisiya mbumba, mbakwata Yezu m'mwadia mukhakhala iye na myedia inango izinji ikhantoera.
\vref MRK.4:37
\v 37
\vt Pikhaenda iwo conzi cikulo ca mphepocalamuka, mabinbi makulu akhamenya mbapita mwadia,iwo mbukhafuna kulobzeka.
\vref MRK.4:38
\v 38
\vt Yezu akhagona pyace n'dili mwa mwadia nsolo wace mbukhatsamira nsago.
\vref MRK.4:39
\v 39
\vt
\vref MRK.4:40
\v 40
\vt
\vref MRK.4:41
\v 41
\rcrd MRK 5
\c 5
\s
\p
\vref MRK.5:1
\v 1
\vt Yezu na anyakufhunza ace afika ntunda unango wa bara, ku cisa ca Djerasa/Gerasa.
\vref MRK.5:2
\v 2
\vt Pa ndzidzi unowu udachita yezu m'mwadya, abulukirambo mamuna m'bodzi wakuphtwa na nzimu wakuipa, mbakhaenda kuna Yezu. Mamuna uyu akhabulukira/akhabuluka na pa'masiye.
\vref MRK.5:3
\v 3
\vt Iye akhakhala n'dzinthumbi. pontho akhacimwanika, na unyolo ene myendo, kuti aphatiwe amangwe.
\vref MRK.5:4
\v 4
\vt Kazinji kene akhadamangana unyolo, myendo na mikono ene. mbwenye iye akhathumula basi pyonsene. Na tenepa nkhbe munthu akhankodza kumphata.
\vref MRK.5:5
\v 5
\vt Ntsiku zonsene, masiku na masikati akhakhuwa m;'mapiri na pakati pa dzithumbi, mbakhaphekeka na myala.
\vref MRK.5:6
\v 6
\vt Penepo iye na kuona Yezu kutali, anthamangira mban'godamira/mbamulambira.
\vref MRK.5:7
\v 7
\vt Na tenepa alonga /mbolonga na kukhuwa kuti: Imwe Yezu mwana wa mulungu wa n'k/ n'nkulu/wakulu,musafunji na ine? Ndisakuphemberani na dzina ya Mulugu kuti mukhonde kundigopesa/ kundisanya.
\vref MRK.5:8
\v 8
\vt Mamuna/munlha uyu alonga tenepa, ndi thangwi Yezu akhadalonga kuna iye kuti: «Buluka, muna munthu uyu iwe nzimu wakuipa!»
\vref MRK.5:9
\v 9
\vt Pontho Yezu ambvunza munthu uyu kuti iwe dzina yako ndiwe ani? Iye atawira: Dzina yanga ndine mwinji, thangwi ndife azinji.
\vref MRK.5:10
\v 10
\vt Na tnepa iye akhathimiza basi na kumpemba Yezu mbakhalonga: Lekani kutibulusa/kutithamangisa pa cisa cino.
\vref MRK.5:11
\v 11
\vt Phapopenepo pa dhudzi, ukhasodza pa phiri nkumbiwa nkhuba.
\vref MRK.5:12
\v 12
\vt Na tenepa mizimu yakuipa yaphembakuna Yezu kuti:« Tisiyeni pyathu tikapite munkumbi wa nkhumba/n'khumbi.
\vref MRK.5:13
\v 13
\vt Penepo Yezu aatawira. Na tenepa mizimu yakuipa yabuluka muna mamuna/munthu,yapita mna khumba./mu nkumbi wa mkhumba penepo nkhumba zonsene zikhalipo dhudzi na pikwi piwiri. N'kumbi onsene wa nkhumba watoma kutamangira m'bara, nkumba zonsene mbazimala kufa m'madzi.
\vref MRK.5:14
\v 14
\vt Penepo amakankhumba onsene amala kuthawa mbaenda mbamwadza mphangwa zenezi mu ndzinda na m'mmidzi ya n'khundu n'khundu mwace. Anthu azunji aenda kaona ninji pikhadacitika.
\vref MRK.5:15
\v 15
\vt Anthu pakufika pano Yezu aona mamuna akhakhala na mizimu mizinji yakuipa, penepo agumanika mbali mwadidi, na nzeru zace za kubaliwa/mwakubaliwa. Mbakhakhala pansi na matako ace na nguwo zace m'manungo. Na kupiona anthu agopserwa napyo.
\vref MRK.5:16
\v 16
\vt Na tenepa ale akhadapiona na maso awo atoma kulonga pyonsene kuna anthu pire pikhadacitika kuna mamuna akhali na mizimu yakuipa, na kuli nkhumba.
\vref MRK.5:17
\v 17
\vt enepo anthu atoma kumphemba Yezu kutiiye abuluke n'dziko mwawo.
\vref MRK.5:18
\v 18
\vt Ndzidzi ukhapakira Yezu m'mwadiya, abwera mamuna ule akhakhala na mizimu yakuipa, kudza kaphamba yezu kuti aende na iye.
\vref MRK.5:19
\v 19
\vt Mbenye Yezu akhonda mbampanga kuti: Ndoko kwanu ndoko ukalonge/ kalonge/ nkaapange/kaapange abale, na ntsisi zidakubvera iye.
\vref MRK.5:20
\v 20
\vt Na tenepa mamuna abuluka mbaenda mbalonga pyonsene pikhadacitira Yezu,m'midzinda khumiinacemerwa dekapoli: penepo anthu onsene adzumatirwa napyo.
\vref MRK.5:21
\v 21
\vt Yezu awambuka jontho kuenda ntunda unango wa bara. pidafika iye pa gombe, pandzidzi ubodzi ene mwinji wa anthu watoma kugumanyikana pontho n'khundu mwace.
\vref MRK.5:22
\v 22
\vt Penepo, mamuna m'bodzi anacemerwa Djairu, ntsogoleri n'bodzi wa nyumba yakuphembera, anfendedzera Yezu mban'godamira.
\vref MRK.5:23
\v 23
\vt Mbapemphemba mbalonga kuti:Mwananga wankadzi alikufa. bwerani mudze kamuikhe manja na kumphemberera toera awange, apulumuke.
\vref MRK.5:24
\v 24
\vt Na tenepa Yezu aenda na iye. penepo mwinji wa anthu akhatoera ukhadadzala kakamwe, kufikira Yezu mbakhafinyana na anthu.
\vref MRK.5:25
\v 25
\vt Penepo akhalio n'kadzi m'bodzi akhadza mbadwala nthenda yakubuluka ciropa, pa pyaka khumi na piwiri mbalinayo.
\vref MRK.5:26
\v 26
\vt pontho akhdaona nyatwa zikulu na kubvunga pedzi pyonsene pikhali na iye na kusaka akonzi thangwi nthenda yace ikhatekereratu kuenda kutsogolo.
\vref MRK.5:27
\v 27
\vt Nkodzi na kubva mbiri ya yezu abwera na kupapatula pakati pa mbumba ya anthu, mbafendezera Yezu nduli mwce.
\vref MRK.5:28
\v 28
\vt Thagwi iye akhalonga ekhaene kuti; Ndingakwanisa kun'gweza nguwo zace basi, ndnawanga.
\vref MRK.5:29
\v 29
\vt Padzidzi ubodzi-bodzi abva kuti ciropankhabe kubulukabve. Pontho abva kuti nthenda yaceya wanga.
\vref MRK.5:30
\v 30
\vt Penepo pene Yezu abva kuti mphabvu zace zapunguka muna iye. Na tenepa iye azungunuka kuna mbumba, mbabvudzisa: Mbani andigweza nguwo zanga?
\vref MRK.5:31
\v 31
\vt Anyakufhunza ace antawira mbalonga kuti: Imwe nkhabe ona kuti mbumba yonsene iyi isafinyana na imwe andigweza?
\vref MRK.5:32
\v 32
\vt Mbenye Yezu akhalang'anisa basi n'khundu mwace, toera aone mbani akhadangweza.
\vref MRK.5:33
\v 33
\vt Penepo nksdzi na kudziwa pikhadacitika na iye atoma kudzadzamira na kugopa/ mbafendezerayezu, mbangodamira, mbampanga pyonsene, mbakhonda kum'bisira ninga mudacitika ipyo.
\vref MRK.5:34
\v 34
\vt Na tenepe yezu apanga nkadzi kuti:mwananga, kukhulupira kwako kwakupulumusa. Ndiko na kusanzaya nthenda yako yawanga.
\vref MRK.5:35
\v 35
\vt Yezu mbdzati kumala kulonga afika anthu anango a ku nyumba ya ntsogoleri wa nyumba ya kumphembera, anacemerwa Djairo, mbalonga kuna iye kuti: mwamuna wa ntsikana afa. Munasanyiranji mphunzisi?
\vref MRK.5:36
\v 36
\vt Mbwenye yezu akhonda kusalakana pyonsene ipyo mbalonga kuna djairo kuti:leka kugopa khulupira.
\vref MRK.5:37
\v 37
\vt Penepo yezu abuluka basi na peduru, Djakobo/ na m'bale wace anacemerwa Djuwau. Akhonda kuperekerwa na anango anthu.
\vref MRK.5:38
\v 38
\vt Na tenepa Yezu aenda ku nyumba ya Djairo mbagumana anthu azinji apcisa mbakhakhuwa na kulira.
\vref MRK.5:39
\v 39
\vt Yezu apita n'nyumba mbabvunza anthu akhalimwenemu kuti: m'khuwo onow na ciriro ceneci nchanji?/N'tsikana hadafa tayo, mbenye ali kugona.
\vref MRK.5:40
\v 40
\vt Na tenepa anthu atoma kunseka. mbwenye Yezu aabulusisa anthu onsene akhali n'nyumba, mbapita iye basi,na anyakuphunza ace atatu, na baba na mai wace mwana, m'paka kumbuto kukhagona mwana.
\vref MRK.5:41
\v 41
\vt Penepo yezu amphata manja ace mwana, mbampanga: Thalita kumi- uku ndiko kubveka mwana/ mwanawe! Ine ndine anakupanga/ndisakupanga lamuka!
\vref MRK.5:42
\v 42
\vt Penepo pene, mwana akhali na pyaka khumi na piwiri alamukiratu mbafamba penepyo anthu onsene adzumatirwa napyo.
\vref MRK.5:43
\v 43
\vt Mbwenye yezu aapanga kuti akhonde kupanga munthu penepyo. Pakumala aapanga kuti apase mwana cakudya.
\rcrd MRK 6
\c 6
\s
\p
\vref MRK.6:1
\v 1
\vt Pakubuluka penepo Yezu na anyakuphunza ace akwatana mbaenda ku dziko kwawo ku Nazareti.
\vref MRK.6:2
\v 2
\vt Pakufika ntsiku ya sabudu Yezu atoma kuphunzisa mu nyumba ya kupephera. Azinji anthu akhamubvesera pikhafhunzisaiye, akhadzuma mbakhalonga kui: Pyabuluka kupi pyonsene ipi? Mbani ampasa/ucenjeriunowu /Apaswa na aniucenjeri unowu? Asacita tani pirengo penepyo?!
\vref MRK.6:3
\v 3
\vt Kodi siye unowu tayu karapinteiro mwana wa Mariya? Pontho abale ace amamuna siwo ale anacemerwa yakobo, Zuze Djuda na Simau? anakadzi ace siwo ale anakhala na ife kuno? na tenepa iwo onsene akhonda kufuna/ kuntawira.
\vref MRK.6:4
\v 4
\vt Na tenepa Yezu alonga kuna iwo kuti: Mporifeta asafuniwa ku dziko kwace, pakati pa anzace a pacisa na pa abale ace a pa nyumba.
\vref MRK.6:5
\v 5
\vt na tenepa yezu akhakhonda kucita pilengo. Mbwenye akhatawira basi kuwangisa atenda na kuwaikha manja.
\vref MRK.6:6
\v 6
\vt yezu azumatirwa na abale ace na thangwi yakukhonda kutawira kwawo. na tenepa anyerazera pyace kuenda kafhunzisa anthu anango a n'khundu.
\vref MRK.6:7
\v 7
\vt Penepo yezu acemera anyakufhunza ace khumi na awiri, mbaatuma awiri-awiri, pontho na kuwapasa mphabvu za kuthamangisa mizimu ya kuipa.
\vref MRK.6:8
\v 8
\vt Na tenepa yezu aapanga kuti: Paulendo wanu lekani kukwata pinthu ninga ipi: n'kate,budu na kobiri, n'cuno mwanu.Mbwenye kwatani golomondo basi.
\vref MRK.6:9
\v 9
\vt Pontho yezu athimiza na kuapanga kuti: fambani na nsapato zanu, mbwenye lekani kukwata nguwo ziwiri.
\vref MRK.6:10
\v 10
\vt yezu apanga pontho kuti: Mungapitiswa n'nyumba ibodzi, khalani mwenemu mpaka kubuluka kwanu.
\vref MRK.6:11
\v 11
\vt ungakhonda kutambirwa na anthu panafika imwe, pontho iwo mbkhonda kukubverani, pakubuluka kwanu gubudzani fhumbi manyalo anu, ninga cidzndikiro ca kuacenjeza.
\vref MRK.6:12
\v 12
\vt Na tenepa anyakufhunza a Yezu abuluka mbaenda mbalonga kuna anthu kuti achunyuke kudawa kwawo.
\vref MRK.6:13
\v 13
\vt Mbakhabulusa mizimu mizinji yakuipa, pontho na kuangisa atenda azinji na kuadzoza mafuta.
\vref MRK.6:14
\v 14
\vt pyonsne ipyo pyafika m'makutu mwa mambo Herodi. Thangwi mbiri ya yezu ikhadafika monsene . Anthu anango akhalonga kuti djwau batixta alamuka pa akufa. ndi thangwi ineyo iye Yezu anamphambvu za kucita pirengo penepyo.fs
\vref MRK.6:15
\v 15
\vt Anango akhalonga kuti ndi Eliasi. Anthu anango akhalonga kuit iye ndi m'bodzi wa aporofeta akale./ndi m'bodzi wa mpoorofeta wakale.
\vref MRK.6:16
\v 16
\vt Herodi nakubva pyonsene ipyo alonga kuti: Ndimo mwene uyu ndiyedi Djuwau batixta, ule akhadagwanda ene nsolo. Alamuka pa kufa.
\vref MRK.6:17
\v 17
\vt Ndimo mwene, herodi akhadamangisadi djuwau batixta mbamuikhisa n'kaidi.Penepyo apicita na thangwi ya herodi, nkadzi wa dafutu bale wace anacemerwa Filipe. Iye herodi akhadankwata mbacita nkadzi.
\vref MRK.6:18
\v 18
\vt Na thangwi eneyo, djuwau batixta akhadampanga Herodi kuti: Sipyiadidi tayu kucita banja na nkadzi wa bale wako.
\vref MRK.6:19
\v 19
\vt Na tenepa nkadzi wa Herodi, atoma kupitirwa na nyongo mbaipirwa na Djuwau batixta, mbakhafuna kumphesa.Mbwenye akhapicimwana/pikhacimwanika.
\vref MRK.6:20
\v 20
\vt Pinango Herodi akhagopa djuwau batixta. thangwi iye akhapiziwa kuti djuwau ndi munthu wakulungama pontho ndi munthu wa mulungu. Na tenepa akhambvunulira. Angalonga na iye, Herodi akhadzudzumika napyo. Mbwenye akhakomerwa na kubva pikhalonga djuwau.
\vref MRK.6:21
\v 21
\vt Mbwenye waza kagumanika ndzidzi wadidi kuna Herodia. Herodi, mamuna wa Herodia pidacita iye caka acitisa mphwandu ikulu kakamwe. Acemeresa akulu-akuli a utongi wace na asogolere a anyakhondo na anthu anango akulu akubvekera a mu dziko ya Galileya, toera kudya nanthu /pabadzi mphwandu.
\vref MRK.6:22
\v 22
\vt Penepo mwana wace herodi wa nkadzi apita nthando mbabvina pikulu kakamwe.Na tenepa kubvina kwace kwasanzaisa Herodi baba wace na akulu onsene akhalipenepo mambo Herodi na kukomerwa ampanga mwana wace kuti; Ndipembe pinafuna iwe, ine ndinakupasa.
\vref MRK.6:23
\v 23
\vt Pontho baba athimiza kulonga na kudubira kuti: Ndinakupasa pyonsene pinandiphemba iwe, na phindi ene ya dziko yanga.
\vref MRK.6:24
\v 24
\vt Mwana ntsikana abuluka mbaenda kabvunza mai wacekuti: ndinaphemba nji? mai wace antawira kuti: phemba nsolo wa Djuwau Batixta.
\vref MRK.6:25
\v 25
\vt Na tenepa ntsikana abwera na kuthamanga mbaenda kuna mambo Herodi mbampanga kuti: ndisafuna kuti mundipase cincino nsolo wa Djuwau Batixta, n'ndiro.
\vref MRK.6:26
\v 26
\vt Penepo mambo atsukwala napyo pikulu. Mbenye acimwena kukhondera na thangwi ya cidumbiriro cikhadacita iye pamaso pa akulu onsene akhali pa phwandu.
\vref MRK.6:27
\v 27
\vt Na tenepo mambo atuma nyakhondo wace na mwantsanga toera am'bweresere nsolo wa Djuwau. Penepo nyakhondo alamuka mbaenda kagwanda nsolo wa djuwau n'kaidi.
\vref MRK.6:28
\v 28
\vt Penepo nyakhondo abweresa nsolo mu n'ndiro mbanpasa ntsikana. Iembo ntsikana mbaenda kapasambo mai wace.
\vref MRK.6:29
\v 29
\vt Anyakufhunza a djuwau batixta na kubva mphangwa zenezi aenda kakwata manungo anyakwenda mbaikhisa/mbaenda kaiikhisa/kaaikhisa /kaikhisa.
\vref MRK.6:30
\v 30
\vt Pa kubwerera kwa anyakufhunza a Yezu pa ulendo ukhaacita iwo, agumanyikana na Yezu mbalonga pyonsene pikhadacitika iwo na pikhadafhunzisa iwo.
\vref MRK.6:31
\v 31
\vt Penepo pakhagumanika anthu azinji. Awa akhabwera awa akhaenda. na tnepo yezu na anyakufhunza ace akhausowa ndzidzi wa kupuma na wa kudya ene. Na tenepa Yezu aapanga anyakufhunza ace kuti: atendeni pakhundu pang'ono, pathu tekha toera mukapume.
\vref MRK.6:32
\v 32
\vt Na tenepa iwo abuluka onsene, mbakwira m'bote mbaenda pa m'mbuto ibodzi yawo wokha.
\vref MRK.6:33
\v 33
\vt Mbwenye anthu azinji aaona kwenda kwawo. Na kuadzindikira kuti ndiwo, abuluka m'midzinda monsene mbaenda mbathamanga na myendo, na ntunda m'paka pa mbuto eneyo.Anthu ndiwo adathanga kufika kupita kupiringana anyakufhunza a Yezu.
\vref MRK.6:34
\v 34
\vt Pa kuchita m'bote, Yezu aona kuntunda mwinji ukulu wa anthu, mbakhala ninga mabira akusowa nkumbidzi penepo Yezu aabverantsisi mbatoma koapfunzisa pnthu pizinji.
\vref MRK.6:35
\v 35
\vt Pikhadka kunja, anyakupfunza a Yezu abwera kuna iye mbalonga kuti: kuno ndi kutsanga nkhabe pinthu, pontho dzuwa iri kudika.
\vref MRK.6:36
\v 36
\vt Siyani anthu aende pyawo m'mnda na mpisa toera aende kagule pyakudya pina funa iwo.
\vref MRK.6:37
\v 37
\vt Mbwenye yezu aataawira kuti: apaseni imwe cakudya. mphapo iwo atawira kuti: toera kugula mikate inakwana kuli anthu onsene awa, tisafunika tikhake na madzana mawiri a mbondo /cobiri.
\vref MRK.6:38
\v 38
\vt Penepo Yezu athimidza na kuabvunza mbalonga kuti: "imwe muna mikate mingasi?"Iwo atawira kuti;" ife tina mikate mixanu, na nyama ziwira zam'madzi "
\vref MRK.6:39
\v 39
\vt Na tenepa Yezu aapanga anyakupfunz ace kuti; Gumanyisani mbumba ikhale pace-pace/nsoka-nsoka, pansi pa tsanga ya cimbanjiri.
\vref MRK.6:40
\v 40
\vt penepo onsene akhala pansi mbagumanana nsoka-nsoka wa makumaxanu, dzana wa anthu.
\vref MRK.6:41
\v 41
\vt Pkumala, Yezu akwata mikate ire mixanu na nyama ziwiri zire za m'madzi mbalang'ana kudzul mbaiphemberera. Pidamaiye mbakwata mikate ire mixanu mbaimenya-menya mbaipasa anyakupfunza ace toera iwo aigawirembo/aigazembo mbumba. Pakumala akwatambo nyama mbaigawizambo anthu sawa-sawa.
\vref MRK.6:42
\v 42
\vt onsene adya mbakhuta.
\vref MRK.6:43
\v 43
\vt Pontho akwanisa kuzaza pitundu khumi na piwiri na manyezo akhadasala mikate na nyama za m'madzi.
\vref MRK.6:44
\v 44
\vt Anthu akhadadya akhalipo amuna akukwana pikwi pixanu pya amuna nsoka ukhadadya ukhalipo pikwi pixanu pya amuna.
\vref MRK.6:45
\v 45
\vt Pakumala penepo Yezu aapanga anyakupfunza ace kuti: apite m'bote, atsogole aende ku dziko ya bitisayida akwire n'tunda unango wa bara ya galileya. Betisaida, kuli anthu kuti iye asale mbabulisa anthu/mbumba.
\vref MRK.6:46
\v 46
\vt Pidamala iye kupanganizana na mbumba,akwira mbaenda pa phiri kaphembera.
\vref MRK.6:47
\v 47
\vt Pakudoka dzuwa bote ikhagumanika basi pakati pa bara.Mbwenye Yezu akhagumanika ekhene pa ntunda.
\vref MRK.6:48
\v 48
\vt Mangwana mwace, m'bamba kuca, yezu aona kuti anyakupfunza ace aneta na kucapa bote yawo, thangwi akhaenda kukhabuluka/kukhabwera mphepo. Na tenepa Yezu aagwerera mbafamba padzulu pa madzi, mbakhaena kuna iwo. Mudafika iye dhuzi acita ninga asafuna kuapitirira.
\vref MRK.6:49
\v 49
\vt Anyakupfunza ace pidamuona iwo/na kumuona mbafamba padzulu pa madzi atoma kukhuwa na kugopa.Thangwi akhanyerazera kuti ndi ciphoko.
\vref MRK.6:50
\v 50
\vt Na mwenemo onsene akhadamuona, atutumuka napyo. Mbwenye Yezu aapangiratu kuti: khalani na cipapo/pirirani!ndine pano lekani kugopa.
\vref MRK.6:51
\v 51
\vt Penepo Yezu akwira m'bote mbakhala pabodzi na anyakupfunza ace. Penepo mphepo yamatama, na tenepa anyakupfunza onsene azumatirwa napyo.
\vref MRK.6:52
\v 52
\vt Thangwi cirengo ca mikate hakhadzati kucibvesa. Pontho mitima yawo ikhadauma.
\vref MRK.6:53
\v 53
\vt Pidawambuka iwo ntunda unango wa Genesareti asamisa bote yawo pa ntunda.
\vref MRK.6:54
\v 54
\vt Pidapandira iwo m 'bote, penepo pene anthu anzindikira Yezu.
\vref MRK.6:55
\v 55
\vt Mphangwa za kufika kwace yezu, za mwazika na mwansanga pa cisa cenaci. Na tenepa mbuto zonsene mukhabuluka atenda m'makha, mbaendeswa kuna Yezu.
\vref MRK.6:56
\v 56
\vt Mbuto zonsene zikhapata Yezu, kutomera m'midzinda, peno m'pisa peno m'midzi, anthu onsene akhazesa atenda awo kuna Yezu, mbakhaphemba kuti aasiye atenda awo an'khuye/agwedze/angwedze basi nguwo zace. Na tenepa atenda onsene akhan'khuya akhawangadi/ akhawangiswadi.
\rcrd MRK 7
\c 7
\s
\p
\vref MRK.7:1
\v 1
\vt Ntsiku inango afalisi, na anyakudziwisa amwambo anango akhabuluka ku djerusalema, agumanyikana pabodzi pene na Yezu.
\vref MRK.7:2
\v 2
\vt Iwo akhaona kuti anyakupfunza anango a yezu akhadya mbakhonda kutoeza mwambo wa kusamba manja.
\vref MRK.7:3
\v 3
\vt thangwi adjuda na afalisi nkhabe kudya mbasati/mbadzati samba pyadidi manja, tora kutoeza mwambo wa akulu ao akele.
\vref MRK.7:4
\v 4
\vt Angalewerera buluka kagula pithu, asasamba piadidi pyene manja mbasati/mbadzati kudya na mitemo mizinji inango iwo akhaiphinduza kudza myambo mbakhaitoeza mwadidi, ninga matsukiro anango a makhomico, mbale wa mikua.
\vref MRK.7:5
\v 5
\vt Na thangwi eneyo, afalisi na anyakudzwisa a mwambo abvunzise yezu.«thangwi yanji anyakufunza ako nkhabe kutoeza ntemo wa akulu athu akale, mbadya mbakhonda samba manja?»
\vref MRK.7:6
\v 6
\vt yezu aatawira tenepa:«anyauthambi!Ndimomwenedi pikhalonga mporofeta Isayakuli imwe, mbalemba tenepa mphangwa za Mulungu.Mbumba iyi isadilemedza na miromo yao basi mbwnye ntima wao uli kutali na ine.
\vref MRK.7:7
\v 7
\vt asandilambira papezi, thangwi asafunisa cifinzo ca anthu.
\vref MRK.7:8
\v 8
\vt Iwe musapwaza mwambo wa mulungu toera mubvere mafunisiro a anthu.
\vref MRK.7:9
\v 9
\vt Mbathimiza kulonga tenepa: kazanji kene musasaka nthangwi kuti mbamutoeza pyanu mitemo yanu.
\vref MRK.7:10
\v 10
\vt Ndimo mwene kuti muzesi afunzisa tenepa: Lemedza baba wako na mai wako.Alonga pontho kuti: ule ana xola baba wace peno mai wace asatongwa kuti aphiwe.
\vref MRK.7:11
\v 11
\vt Mbwenye imwe musafunzisa kuti: Munthu ngakhala na pinthu toera kuplhedza napyo baba wace na mai wace angacherenga, pinthu penepyo iye akhadamala kudumbira kale kuti apipereke kuna Mulungu.
\vref MRK.7:12
\v 12
\vt Munthu onowo nkhabebve tairiswa mphedza baba wace na mai wace.
\vref MRK.7:13
\v 13
\vt Tenepa imwe musapwaza mwambo wa mulungu, mbamwachinja na mafunzisiro anu anafunzisa imwe bulukira kuno a baba mpaka kuna ana.Na pizinji pinango ninga penepi pinacita imwe
\vref MRK.7:14
\v 14
\vt yezu aacemera ponto anthu mbaavunza tenepa: «Bveserani pyonsene pinakupangani ine mupiikhe m'makutu.»
\vref MRK.7:15
\v 15
\vt Cinthu cinapita m'manungo mwa munthu nkhabe kunswipisa. Mbwenye cirecinabuluka nkati mwamunthu ndico cinanswipisa.
\vref MRK.7:16
\v 16
\vt Ana makutu mbabvesere.
\vref MRK.7:17
\v 17
\vt Yezu munamwazana iye na mbumba,apita n'nyumba anyakufunza ace mbanvunza kuti usalongeranji nsanje onowo?
\vref MRK.7:18
\v 18
\vt Iye aatawira tenepa; « Na imwe ene mudapibveserambo tayu?» Nkhabe dziwa imwe kuti cidadia munthu peno cinamwa iye nkhabe kunswipisa.
\vref MRK.7:19
\v 19
\vt Thangwi penepi nkhabe pita muntima, pisaenda ncifu pingamala mbapibuluka pontho m'manungo. [Na mafala awa Yezu akhapangisa kuti pyakudia pyonsene mphyadidi.]
\vref MRK.7:20
\v 20
\vt Yezu athimiza pontho kulonga tenepa:«cinabuluka muna munthu ndico cinanswipisa.»
\vref MRK.7:21
\v 21
\vt Nthangwi muntima mwace ndimo munabuluka manyerezero akuipa, ninga cimaso-maso, umbava kuplha munthu.
\vref MRK.7:22
\v 22
\vt Pya lukwale, kuumirwa, kuipa ntima, psweda, kuzunda, bibvu, utatawa, kupikuza na kukupwa.
\vref MRK.7:23
\v 23
\vt Pyonsene ipi pyakuipa pisabuluka mu ntima mwa munthu, penepi ndipyo pinanswipisa.
\vref MRK.7:24
\v 24
\vt Yezu pidabuluka iye kweneko aenda ku ndzinda wa Tiru na wa Sidony. Apita n'nyumba thangwi iye akafuna tayu kuti anthu andziwe kuti ali kupi , mbwenye acimwana bisala ndzidzi ukulu ene.
\vref MRK.7:25
\v 25
\vt Nkazi m'bodzi akhali na mwana wace wa nkazi akhabva mbiri ya Yezu, ansaka mban'godamira m'myendo mwace thangwi mwana wace akhali na nzimu wa kuipa.
\vref MRK.7:26
\v 26
\vt Iye akhali n'djuda tayu akhali wa ku dziko ya FINISIA. Aphemba kuna Yezu kuti anbuluse nzimu wakuipa ukhali na mwana wace.
\vref MRK.7:27
\v 27
\vt Mbwenye Yezu antawira tenepa: «Cakutoma sya ana akhute thangwi sipadidi tayu kwata nkate wa ana mbatipasa anambwa.»
\vref MRK.7:28
\v 28
\vt Nkazi atawira tenepa: Ande mbuya,« mbwenye anabwa asalokoterambo manyezo anagwisa ana pansi.»
\vref MRK.7:29
\v 29
\vt Penepo Yezu ampanga tenepa: Ndimo mwene mudatawira iwe! Bwerera wende kunyumba kwako thangwi nzimu wa kuipa wabuluka muna mwanako.
\vref MRK.7:30
\v 30
\vt Nkazi abwerera mbaenda kunyumba kuace mbagumana mwanace akhagona pa talimba,nthangwi nzimu wa kuipa ukhadabuluka.
\vref MRK.7:31
\v 31
\vt Yezu abuluka pontho ku ndzinda wa Tiru na wa Sidony, mbaenda mpaka ku Bara ya Galileya mbagwanda mpaka ku cisa ca Dekapuly.
\vref MRK.7:32
\v 32
\vt Kweneko anthu andzesera munthu m'bodzi wakukhonda kubva pontho iye akhalonga mwadidi mwene tayu, mbaphemba kuti yezu amwikhe djanja yace toera ankonze.
\vref MRK.7:33
\v 33
\vt Yezu ankwata mamuna ule mbathaukira na iye kutali pan'gono na anthu.Aikha pyala pyace m'makutumwace mbaukhwaza mata pa lirime yace.
\vref MRK.7:34
\v 34
\vt Buluka penepo akwiza maso kudzulu mbapuma na mphabvu mbalonga tenepa:Efata! ndiko kubveka:«Fungilika.»
\vref MRK.7:35
\v 35
\vt Makutu amamuna ule afunguka, na muansanga lirime yace yasudzuka, mbatoma kulonga mwadidi mwene.
\vref MRK.7:36
\v 36
\vt Penepo Yezu aapanga anthu kuti aleke kupilonga kuna anango.Mbwenye pikaakhondesa iye, iwo akhapilongeratu kakamwe.
\vref MRK.7:37
\v 37
\vt Onsene akhadzumatirwa napyo mbalonga tenepa:«Asacita pyadidi kuna anthu onsene. Asafungula makutu ale anakhonda kubva na ale anakhonda longa asalonga.!»
\rcrd MRK 8
\c 8
\s
\p
\vref MRK.8:1
\v 1
\vt Pakupita ntsiku pan'gono waoneka/wagumanika pontho mwinji wa anthu patsogolo pa Yezu.Na thangwi yakusoeka cakudya Yezu acemera anyakupfunza paapanga kuti.
\vref MRK.8:2
\v 2
\vt Ndina ntsisi na anthu awa thangwi anaine ntsiku zitatu, pontho pano nkhabe cakudya.
\vref MRK.8:3
\v 3
\vt Ndingaabweza m'midzi mwawo tenepa na njala, anakomokera njira. Thangwi anango azinji abuluka kutali.
\vref MRK.8:4
\v 4
\vt Mbenye anyakupfunza ace alonga kuti: Tinaigumana kupi mikate ace inakwana anthu onsene awa, n'thando ninga muno?
\vref MRK.8:5
\v 5
\vt Yezu aabvunza kuti: Muna mikate mingasi penepo? iwo atawira kuti: tina mikate minomwe.
\vref MRK.8:6
\v 6
\vt Na tenepa Yezu aipanga mbumba kuti ikhale pansi, pakumala penepo akwata mikate minomwe ire, mbaiphemberera mbaipasa anyakupfunza ace, toera iwo aigawirembo mbumba.
\vref MRK.8:7
\v 7
\vt Zikhalipombo nyama pang'ono za m'mdzi, Yezu azikwata mbaziphembererambo sawa-sawa, mbazipasa anyakupfunza ace, toera iwo azigawirembo.
\vref MRK.8:8
\v 8
\vt Onsene adya mbakhuta. pa kumala akwanisa kudzaza pitundu pinomwe na manyedzo a kusala a mikate.
\vref MRK.8:9
\v 9
\vt Anthu akhadadya akhathamangira ku pikwi pinai pakumala penepo Yezu aibweza mbumba mbienda
\vref MRK.8:10
\v 10
\vt Yezu akwira m'bote na anyakupfunza ace mbaenda cisa ca Dalimanuta.
\vref MRK.8:11
\v 11
\vt Penepo afika afarisi anango, mbatoma kuketesana na Yezu thangwi iwo akhafuna kumulesera kuti aapase cizindikiro cinapangiza kuti Iye atumwa na mulungu.
\vref MRK.8:12
\v 12
\vt Mbwenye Yezu asiribza pikulu mbalonga kuti: thangwi yanji anthu acincino /antsiku zino asafuna cizindikiro? Mphapo ine ndinakupangani pakweca kuti anthu anawa ine nkhabe kudzakaapasa cizindikiro cibodzi.
\vref MRK.8:13
\v 13
\vt Penepo yezu aasiya,mbapakira pyace pontho m'bote, mbaenda n'tando unango wa bara.
\vref MRK.8:14
\v 14
\vt Anyakupfunza a Yezu akhadaduwala kukwata mikate. Na tenepa m'bote akhali na nkate ubodzi basi.
\vref MRK.8:15
\v 15
\vt Penepo Yezu aacenjeza mbaapanga/mbalonga kuti: Citani mpolena nsanga wa afarisi na wa herodi.
\vref MRK.8:16
\v 16
\vt Mpapo, anyakupfunza na kubva penepyo akhaketesana okha-okha, mbakhlonga kuti: Ndi thangwi yakusoeka mikate.
\vref MRK.8:17
\v 17
\vt Mbwenye Yezu na kudzwa manyeredzero awo, aabvunza kuti; thangwi yanji muli kuketesana na kusowa mikate? mudzati tayu kupibvesesa? mumoyo basi mitima yanu yakuuma?
\vref MRK.8:18
\v 18
\vt Muna maso nkhabe kuona? muna makuto nkhabe kubva? Imwe nkhabe kukumbuka,
\vref MRK.8:19
\v 19
\vt mikate mixanu idagawirene anthu akukwana pikwi pixanu? pitundu pingasi pidadzaza imwe na manyezo akusala a mikate? Iwo atawira kuti khumi na piwiri.
\vref MRK.8:20
\v 20
\vt pontho, pitundu pingasi pyakudzala na manyezo adagumanya imwe amikate minomwe adagawira ine pikwi pinai pya anthu? iwo atawira kuti ndi pinomwe.
\vref MRK.8:21
\v 21
\vt Yezu aatawira kuti mudzati kupibvesa basi tayu?
\vref MRK.8:22
\v 22
\vt Yezu na anyakupfunza ace afika ku dziko ya Betisaida penepo anthu anango abwerambo na ntenda wawo m'bodzi wa boliboli, mbaphemba Yezu kuti akhuye.
\vref MRK.8:23
\v 23
\vt Penepo Yezu aphata nkono wa boliboli mbamulamusa mbaenda naye kunja kwa ndzinda. kweneko Yezu aphula mata mbakhwaza m maso mwace mbamuikha manja mbabvunza kuti: uli kuona pinthu:
\vref MRK.8:24
\v 24
\vt Mamuna afungula maso ace mbalonga kuti ande ndirikuona anthu. Mbwenye ndiri kuwaona ninga miti yakufamba.
\vref MRK.8:25
\v 25
\vt Na tenepa Yezu amuikha pontho manja m'maso mwace kubulukira penepo, mamuna mbatoma kuona mwadidi na kutali pyonsene pikhali n'khundu mwace
\vref MRK.8:26
\v 26
\vt
